---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/baseLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = 'Contact Me';
---
<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  
  <div class="container col-xl-10 col-xxl-8 px-4">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-lg-5 py-5">
      
      <div class="col-lg-7 text-center text-lg-start">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis">Let's Connect!</h1>
        <p class="lead mb-4">Hey! I'm excited to connect with people. Whether you have an idea in mind, want to collaborate on a project, or just want to have a chat, I am all ears.</p>
        <h2 class="text-body fw-bold"><span class="me-3">ðŸ“ž</span>How You Can Reach Me</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Feel free to shoot me an email at <a href="mailto:calum.t.fenton@gmail.com">calum.t.fenton@gmail.com</a>. I can't wait to hear from you. Or if you prefer a good old-fashioned conversation then give me a ring at <a href="tel:+353860432063">+353-86-043-2063</a>. I'm always up for a chat.</p>
        <h2 class="text-body fw-bold"><span class="me-3">â˜•</span>Let's Grab a Coffee</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">I'm currently based in Cork city, in Ireland. If you're in the neighboroughood, I'd love to meet up for a coffee, just drop me a message and we can set it up.</p>
        <h2 class="text-body fw-bold"><span class="me-3">ðŸ“§</span>Drop Me a Message</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Have a question, or just want to get in touch? Fill out the contact form and I will get back to you as soon as possible. I can't wait to hear from you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto col-lg-5">
        <form class="p-4 p-md-5 border rounded-3 bg-body-tertiary">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="email">Email Address</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="name@example.com" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="subject">Subject</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="subject" placeholder="Subject">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 mt-4">
                <textarea name="email-content" class="form-control" rows="10" placeholder="Write your message here..." required></textarea>
                <label for="email-content" aria-label="Email content here"></label>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <button class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-dark" type="submit">Send</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>